tr.th: Conclusion and Recommendations based on this report and previous findings known to us

tr.td: All measured parameters are within normal limits. HbA1c is at the upper end of normal, suggesting good glycemic control but close monitoring for diabetes is recommended. Renal function, electrolytes, and metabolic parameters are unremarkable. No acute laboratory abnormalities detected.
